The phenomenon of the &#8216;Bluetooth&#8217; use of the drug Nyaope is common among drug addicts in Tshwane.Nyaope is a dangerous and highly addictive South African street drug. It&#8217;s a fine powder that is usually combined with marijuana and smoked, it can also be snorted or injected. Nyaope is a Heroin based cocktail drugThe process consists of blood being drawn from a drug user who has just got high using nyaope or other narcotics and transferred to another addict via injection.Users have said they&#8217;re aware they risk HIV and other blood diseases but ignore this as they find their addiction too strong to resist.&nbsp;&nbsp;